The <span style="color: #E0B0FF;">**RDP**</span> has been one of our closest allies through the course of the Republic. 

@rdp_green
on-arrival: rdp_relation += 7

Annalena and the greens are supportive of increased collaboration.

@rdp_liberal
on-arrival: rdp_relation += 5

The liberals are more wary of cooperation with us, but are still willing to do it nontheless.


@spd_alone

Whether it is because we *cannot* or *will not*, we do not make ties with other parties at this moment.

